data.text:
Parking: There is free parking adjacent to the library building and in the upper lot.

The Wayland Library is located on Route 126, just north of Route 20, approximately 5 miles west of Route 128.

From the intersection of Route 20 and Route 27, turn north onto Route 126. Bear right at the fork. The library is the large red brick building immediately on the right. See the map of the location below.
